@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy policy · White Stitches";
    ViewData["MetaDescription"] = "How we collect, use and protect your personal information.";
}

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero__inner">
    <span class="eyebrow">Legal · Privacy</span>
    <h1 class="page-hero__title">Privacy policy.</h1>
    <p class="page-hero__lede">How we collect, use and protect your personal information. We respect your privacy and never sell your data.</p>
    <p class="page-hero__meta">Last updated · 1 May 2026</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="policy">
  <div class="policy__inner">
    <aside class="policy__toc" aria-label="On this page">
      <span class="eyebrow">On this page</span>
      <ol class="policy__toc-list">
    <li><a href="#who">Who we are</a></li>
    <li><a href="#what-we-collect">What we collect</a></li>
    <li><a href="#how-we-use">How we use it</a></li>
    <li><a href="#sharing">Who we share it with</a></li>
    <li><a href="#your-rights">Your rights</a></li>
    <li><a href="#retention">How long we keep it</a></li>
    <li><a href="#security">Security</a></li>
    <li><a href="#changes">Changes to this policy</a></li>
      </ol>
    </aside>

    <main class="policy__main">
      <section class="policy-section" id="who">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">Who we are</h2>
        <p>This is the Privacy Policy of <strong>White Stitches Trading Company W.L.L.</strong> ("White Stitches", "we", "us", "our"), a fashion company registered in Kuwait.</p>
         <p>For privacy enquiries, contact our Data Protection Officer at <a href="mailto:privacy@@whitestiches.kw" class="link-inline">privacy@@whitestiches.kw</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="what-we-collect">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">What we collect</h2>
        <p>We collect only what we need to fulfil your orders and improve your experience:</p>
         <ul class="policy-list">
           <li><strong>Identity</strong> — name, date of birth (optional), gender (optional)</li>
           <li><strong>Contact</strong> — email, mobile number, delivery and billing addresses</li>
           <li><strong>Payment</strong> — payment details are tokenised by Tap Payments; we never store card numbers</li>
           <li><strong>Order history</strong> — what you bought, when, where it was shipped</li>
           <li><strong>Behavioural</strong> — pages visited, time on site, items viewed (cookies; see <a href="/cookies" class="link-inline">Cookies Policy</a>)</li>
           <li><strong>Communications</strong> — emails and messages between you and us</li>
         </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="how-we-use">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">How we use it</h2>
        <p>We use your data to:</p>
         <ul class="policy-list">
           <li>Process your orders, payments, shipments and returns</li>
           <li>Provide customer service via email, WhatsApp and phone</li>
           <li>Send order confirmations, tracking, and (if you opt in) marketing</li>
           <li>Personalise product recommendations and improve our site</li>
           <li>Detect fraud and meet legal obligations (tax, finance, anti-fraud)</li>
         </ul>
         <p>We will <strong>never</strong> sell your personal data to third parties.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="sharing">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">Who we share it with</h2>
        <p>We only share data with parties essential to delivering our service:</p>
         <ul class="policy-list">
           <li><strong>Tap Payments</strong> — payment processing (tokenised; we don&rsquo;t see card numbers)</li>
           <li><strong>Couriers</strong> — Aramex, J&amp;T, or local partners for delivery</li>
           <li><strong>Communication platforms</strong> — WhatsApp Business API, email service providers</li>
           <li><strong>Analytics</strong> — Google Analytics (anonymised, with Consent Mode v2)</li>
           <li><strong>Authorities</strong> — when required by Kuwaiti law</li>
         </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="your-rights">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">Your rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
         <ul class="policy-list">
           <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of your data (Account → Profile → Download my data)</li>
           <li><strong>Correct</strong> — update inaccurate information in your account</li>
           <li><strong>Delete</strong> — request deletion of your account (order records retained for legal compliance)</li>
           <li><strong>Object</strong> — to marketing communications via the unsubscribe link in any email</li>
           <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> — turn off any communication channel in Profile preferences</li>
         </ul>
         <p>Email <a href="mailto:privacy@@whitestiches.kw" class="link-inline">privacy@@whitestiches.kw</a> to exercise any of these.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="retention">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">How long we keep it</h2>
        <p>We retain your data only as long as we need to:</p>
         <ul class="policy-list">
           <li><strong>Order records</strong> — 7 years (Kuwaiti tax law)</li>
           <li><strong>Marketing data</strong> — until you unsubscribe</li>
           <li><strong>Account data</strong> — until you delete your account</li>
           <li><strong>Analytics</strong> — 14 months (anonymised)</li>
         </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="security">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">Security</h2>
        <p>We protect your data with industry-standard measures: TLS encryption in transit, encrypted storage at rest, PCI DSS Level 1 payment processing via Tap, and access controls on our team.</p>
         <p>No system is 100% secure. If we ever discover a breach affecting you, we&rsquo;ll notify you within 72 hours.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-section" id="changes">
        <h2 class="policy-section__title">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy as our service and the law evolve. We&rsquo;ll notify you of material changes via email and update the "Last updated" date above.</p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</section>

